{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3e284d12be","title":"五四断想","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"22bd858570","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":1,"articleId":"3e284d12be"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"5eca061dd6","name":"谭天荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fb85aee820","type":"title","text":"五四断想","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"852bb4f5a9","type":"authors","text":"北京大学谭天荣","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"212c05593a","type":"paragraph","text":"旧的悠悠死去，新的悠悠出生，不慌不忙，一个跟一个——这是演化。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"bc9db1d513","type":"paragraph","text":"新的已经来到，旧的还不肯去，新的急了，把旧的挤掉——这是革命。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"d046ca0fe3","type":"paragraph","text":"挤是发展受到阻碍时必然的现象，而新的必然是发展的，能发展的必然是新的，所以青年永远革命的，革命的永远是青年。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"293b5f49c2","type":"paragraph","text":"新的日日壮健着，（量的增长）旧的日日衰老着（量的减毫），壮健的挤着衰老的，没有挤不掉的，所以革命永远是成功的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"e238843864","type":"paragraph","text":"革命成功了，新的变成旧的，又一批新的上来了，旧的倒下来拦住去路，说“我是赶过路程来的，我的血汗不能白流，我该歇下来舒服舒服”，新的说“你的舒服就是我的痛苦，你耽误了我的路程”，又把它挤掉……如此武戏接二连三的演下的，于是革命似乎永远“尚未成功”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"e3ca76b329","type":"paragraph","text":"让曾经新过来的旧的不要只珍惜自己的过去，多多体会别人的将来，自己腰酸腿痛拖不动了，就赶紧让“功成身退”不正是光荣吗？“后生可畏焉知来者之不如今也”这是古训啊！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"d443747c14","type":"paragraph","text":"其实青年并非永远是革命的，“青年永远是革命的”这定理只在“老年永远是不肯让路的”这前提下才成立。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"0255c7ffa1","type":"paragraph","text":"革命可能永远“尚未成功”，几时旧的知趣了到时就功成身退，不致阻碍了新的发展，革命便成功了。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"677e3ad0cc","type":"paragraph","text":"旧的悠悠过去，新的悠悠上来，一个跟着一个，不慌不忙，那天历史走上了演化的常轨，就不再需要变态的革命了。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"3eb0bc341e","type":"paragraph","text":"但目前我们用“挤”来争取“悠悠”，用革命来争取演化“悠悠”是目的，“挤”是达到目的的手段。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"1eb8336040","type":"paragraph","text":"于是，又想到变与乱的问题，变是“悠悠”的演化，乱是挤来挤去的革命，若要不乱挤，就是得悠悠的变，若是该变而不变，那只有挤得你变了。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"c111415bd0","type":"paragraph","text":"子在川上曰“逝者如斯夫，不舍昼夜”，古训也发挥了变的原理。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"5d15f49fd7","type":"subtitle","text":"失  败","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"c856985da0","type":"paragraph","text":"从前我养了一盆宝贵的花儿，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"593040763e","type":"paragraph","text":"为容易，孕了个苞子，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"c1122f140e","type":"paragraph","text":"但老是半含半吐不肯开放","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"e2eeac2797","type":"paragraph","text":"我等得发急，硬把他剥开了，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"6087fe7f88","type":"paragraph","text":"他便一天萎似一天，萎得不像样了，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"ccf210e175","type":"paragraph","text":"如今我要他再关上不能了，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"eb1066ec79","type":"paragraph","text":"我到底没有看见我要看的花！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"4ad15b2903","type":"paragraph","text":"从前我做了一个稀奇的梦，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"a124d0fac5","type":"paragraph","text":"我光嫌他太模糊了，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"0645cc8af8","type":"paragraph","text":"我满不介意，让他震破了，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"1ea9ae21d5","type":"paragraph","text":"我醒的，直等到月落，等到天明，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"f512c58326","type":"paragraph","text":"重织一个新梦既织不成，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"e3cb762e1d","type":"paragraph","text":"便是那个旧的也补不起来了，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"2bce61833d","type":"paragraph","text":"我到底没有做好我要做好的梦！","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"41537bf3d7","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．7．1贴","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"},{"id":"68b7fa7b65","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be"}],"page":{"id":"d53c3f198b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3e284d12be","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}